#Budget2021   National Language Translation Mission will be set up to further boost our regional languages. 100 new Sainik Schools to be created. Other 'umbrella' structures to be created for higher education. More than 15,000 schools will be strengthened under NEP 2020.
#Budget2021  For TN  Major Fishing Harbour to be Developed at Chennai:   Modern Fishing Harbour and Fishing Landing Centre proposed at Chennai (along with 4 other towns)

#Budget2021  Road / Transportation for TN: a. 3500 Kilometres road at Rs.103000 Crores (covering Madurai Kollam and Chittoor-Thatchur) b. In addition, part of Mumbai-Kanyakumari corridor, will be in TN (out of total Rs.65000 Crores) c. Chennai Bangalore & Chennai Salem Expressway

#Budget2021  For TN: Multipurpose Sea Weed Park at Chennai  Natural Sea Weed Resources exist in abundance in Ramanathapuram, Thoothukudi and Pudukottai Districts. It is an emerging Sector. Provide large scale employment and additional income.
